title: Conservative conference: Osborne says 'we are builders'
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device
Conservative conference: Osborne says 'we are builders' 5 October 2015 Last updated at 13:02 BST
George Osborne closed his conference speech by saying it was time to accept responsibility and take on challenges.
And repeating a phrase used several times in his speech, he tells the delegates: "We are the builders."
